Package: ALTRE
Type: Package
Title: Workflow for Identifying Regulatory Elements from Chromatin Accessibility Assay Data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
 person("Elizabeth", "Baskin", email = "Elizabeth.Baskin@osumc.edu", role = "aut"),
 person("Rick", "Farouni", email = "farouni.1@osu.edu", role = "aut"),
 person("Ewy", "Mathe", email = "Ewy.Mathe@osumc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This workflow takes alignment data and hotspot calls from assays of
 open chromatin (ATAC-seq, DNase-seq, and FAIRE-seq) and identifies regulatory
 elements (e.g. enhancers and promoters) that differ across cell and tissue type.
URL: https://github.com/Mathelab/ALTRE
BugReports: https://github.com/Mathelab/ALTRE/issues
